
         about - Read about Clockwork and the cwpol tool
   clear facts - Forget all loaded facts
          fact - Define a fact, ad-hoc
          help - Access Help System
    load facts - Load facts from a file
          load - Load policy manifest from a file
    show facts - Show the loaded facts
    show hosts - List hosts defined in the policy manifest
 show policies - List policies defined in the policy manifest
show resources - List resources defined in a host or policy
          show - Show a full resource definition (for a host or policy)
      use host - Set the current referential context to a named host
    use policy - Set the current referential context to a given policy
          quit - Exit the Policy Explorer

Try 'help <command>' for command-specific help.
